| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6850 — Recovery Inhibition (worldleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5591fef0-b4cc-57e5-821f-ddf243c3f285"
